Z=\frac{-D+L\left\{ \tan\left(\pi+\alpha_{C}-\beta\right)+\tan\alpha_{P}\right\} }{\tan\left(\pi+\alpha_{C}-\beta\right)+\tan\alpha_{P}}\label{eq:Z-complete}
\end{equation}

